snippet.title: Action52 Cheetahmen Commercial.avi
snippet.description: A commercial for Action 52 game cartridge for the Nintendo NES system from the early 90's.  Do not believe it ever aired. I am one of the "college kids" that created most of the games, concepts, and music.  Check out Cheetahmengames.com for more on the history and mystery. I am getting back into making games, Also check out my new music at: https://soundcloud.com/mario-n-gonzalez!
